----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
A very very simple plugin to use the Scoop.it API.
	Links:
		- Scoop.it Developers Home : http://www.scoop.it/dev
		- Scoop.it API Talk : http://groups.google.com/group/scoopit-api-talk
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------


INSTRUCTIONS

Please, follow the instructions bellow:

 - Check if php5-curl is installed
 - Create a "scoopit" directory in the /mod directory
 - Copy/Paste files into the scoopit directory
 - Configure the plugin with the topics you want to watch, the Elgg user you want to be the owner of the posts
 - Enjoy!